Executive: Ravi ji?

Customer: Main beta baat kar rahi hu IndiaMART se.
Executive: Madam bahar hu do din se. Ek number likhiye na us pe contact kar lijiye na.
Customer: Theek hai done.
Customer: Hai wo number mere paas jiske last mein 153 hai wahi na?
Executive: Nahi 99303.
Customer: Ek second rukiye sir. 99303
Executive: 66276.
Customer: Theek hai sir.
